  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Shelter and NFI Assistance for the Most Vulnerable Displaced Populations Identified Through the Emergency Tracking Tool</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In this project, IOM aims to contribute to the improvement of living conditions and protection of conflict-affected populations in the South-West, North-West through the regular production and dissemination of Emergency Tracking Tool (ETT; a component of the Displacement Tracking Matrix) dashboards to support informed humanitarian response planning and assistance and the provision of emergency shelter and non-food item assistance to the most vulnerable newly displaced populations identified through the ETT.</narrative>
  </description>
